    ##                                                             and two translations.  It removes three
    ##                                                             degrees of freedom.  The z axes of csys_1
    ##                                                             and csys_2 are parallel and codirected.
    ##                                                             The origins of csys_1 and csys_2 are in
    ##                                                             a common xy-plane. </description> </item><item><term> 
